<h2>Serving Massachusetts Legal Professionals</h2>
<p>Skerritt Economics &amp; Consulting provides comprehensive forensic economics and business valuation services to attorneys throughout Massachusetts. With extensive experience in the Massachusetts court system and deep understanding of the state's diverse economy, we deliver expert economic analysis that supports successful case outcomes from the Berkshires to Cape Cod.</p>
<p>Our regular appearances in Massachusetts courts include Suffolk quality Court in Boston, Worcester quality Court, Hampden quality Court in Springfield, and federal court in Boston. We understand Massachusetts practice requirements and provide reliable, admissible expert testimony across all 14 counties.</p>
